if you only want to develop a blinkenlet, you will need only the files
build/dist/blinken.jar and the documentation in build/doc

What you have to do:
- if you want to see you blinkenlet, install blib, blinkensim, blinkensim-themes.
- read documentation for class de.blinkenlights.blinkenlet.Blinkenlet in build/doc
- implement your own Blinkenlet (just extends the class)
- contact blinkenlights@lists.ccc.de
